main event: An object was observed on a doorstep in Los Angeles, California on September 7, 1967.
interesting points: The object was described as rock-like and fist-sized,Materials submitted for analysis included a rock-like sample and a metal slug,It was concluded that the large object is probably a piece of ordinary rock,It was suggested that the metal piece is unalloyed iron,The incident generated media interest, although the objects were determined to be common materials.
sighted object: rock-like object and a small metal slug
